<br>
Ok, I see ppl using PoP stones. It use to be journey across continent when I was newbie. Riding boats across, cyclops evading ship. fun stuff. Time when I was really happy when I won that bag thingy from orc named in High pass.<br>
Now... I'm almost lvl 65, with nothing, but EXP in PoP. All I see is PoP Zone, nothing but PoP. Maybe it's just too much exp bonus in PoP zones which made OTHER ZONES COMPLETELY USELESS. No one in Akheva... CT.. is empty as usal today. well there is one group sometimes. Velk is completely empty with light blue spiders.<br>
today, I can't even solo light blue mob. Light blue mob which hit for 300s... /sigh what's up with this? Why does it have to be like this? To sell many pop expansion as possible? Getting 1 parchment in group every 2 hours. I'm lucky if I get one parchment in one day full playing with soloing in PoV. And after I finished hunting, I turn my parchment, and get spell that I already have. <br>
<br>
No quests to do. Sitting in PoS wrecked ship thingy 24/7 just to get one blue today, if I could.<br>
<br>
I try to find something challenge in NEW PoP zone, but it's been weeks. I couldn't find anything fun to do, except hitting for 500+ YOUCANNOTKILLMEWITHOUTSLOW mob.<br>
<br>
Game is broke. but we still play.<br>
Luclin was loot whore<br>
now PoP is Exp whore<br>
<br>
what's to come in next expansion...?<br>
<br>
Tonight, camping early in Ocean of Tears gob island wondering, i almost got killed when I came here at lvl 25.<br>
